
@startuml

' Classes
class Traveller {
  +name: String
  +billingInfo: BillingInfo
  +travelPreferences: List<TravelPreference>
  +reliabilityRating: Double
  +bookings: List<Booking>
}

class BillingInfo {
  +companyName: String
  +address: String
  +creditCardInfo: String
}

class TravelPreference {
  +preferenceType: String
  +value: String
}

class Booking {
  +bookingId: String
  +traveller: Traveller
  +hotel: Hotel
  +startDate: Date
  +endDate: Date
  +numRooms: Integer
  +roomType: String
  +pricePerNight: Double
  +totalCost: Double
  +confirmationStatus: String
  +paymentType: PaymentType
  +cancellationDeadline: Date
  +isConfirmed: Boolean
}

enum PaymentType {
  PREPAID
  PAID_AT_HOTEL
}

class PreliminaryBooking extends Booking {
  +deadline: Date
}

class FinalizedBooking extends Booking {
  +confirmedByHotel: Boolean
  +confirmationDate: Date
}

class Hotel {
  +hotelId: String
  +name: String
  +address: String
  +city: String
  +rating: Integer
  +chain: HotelChain
  +roomsAvailable: Map<Date, RoomAvailability>
}

class RoomAvailability {
  +date: Date
  +roomType: String
  +quantity: Integer
  +isFullyBooked: Boolean
}

class HotelChain {
  +chainId: String
  +name: String
  +hotels: List<Hotel>
}

class SpecialOffer {
  +offerId: String
  +hotel: Hotel
  +pricePerNight: Double
  +additionalBenefits: List<String>
  +validUntil: Date
}

' Relationships
Traveller "1" -- "0..*" Booking : has
Booking "1" -- "1" Hotel : belongs to
Hotel "1" -- "0..*" RoomAvailability : has
Hotel "1" -- "0..1" HotelChain : belongs to
PreliminaryBooking "1" -- "1" Booking : is a
FinalizedBooking "1" -- "1" Booking : is a
Hotel "1" -- "0..*" SpecialOffer : provides
Booking "1" -- "0..*" TravelPreference : includes

@enduml

---

### âś… Explanation of Key Elements:

- **`Traveller`**: Core entity representing users. Has billing info, travel preferences, and bookings.
- **`BillingInfo`**: Contains credit card and company details needed for finalizing a booking.
- **`Booking`**: Base class with common attributes like dates, price, hotel, etc.
- **`PreliminaryBooking` & `FinalizedBooking`**: Subclasses of `Booking` for different stages of booking.
- **`Hotel`**: Represents hotels, including chain affiliation, address, and room availability.
- **`RoomAvailability`**: Tracks available rooms per date and type.
- **`HotelChain`**: Optional grouping of hotels under a brand or chain.
- **`SpecialOffer`**: Offers made by competitor hotels after a preliminary booking.
- **`PaymentType`**: Enum to differentiate between pre-paid and paid-at-hotel options.

